            <h1>Career</h1>

            <p class="fw-hero">
                Originally I started playing Drums at the age of 12 and studied it at the <a href="http://www.musikschule-hy.de/">Musikschule Hoyerswerda</a>,<br>
                under the lead of <a href="http://www.thieme-jens.de/">Jens Thieme</a>.<br>
                Over the years, I also began to play the Guitar and Bass Guitar (self thaught)<br>
                to be able to play and compose my own music, independent from others.<br>
            </p>

            <p class="fw-hero">
                From 2009 to 2014, I was playing Bass Guitar in the Death Metal Band <a href="http://korpus-metal.de">Korpus</a>.<br>
                We played many Gigs in East and South Germany, from Mecklenburg-Vorpommern<br>
                down to Bavaria, and built quite a Fanbase over the years.<br>
                Together we produced two full length records, 'Existenz' and 'Ebendbild'.<br>
            </p>

            <p class="fw-hero">
                Currently, I take a hiatus from Live Music, and produce music for <a href="https://www.facebook.com/Entanglement.music">Entanglement</a> in my spare time.
